reviews_data.review_text:
I was on my way to Charlotte when Google led me to this hidden gem in the beautiful city of Belmont. From the moment I walked in, I could feel the passion of the owner, who personally recommended the coffee-flavored boba tea. And let me tell you - it was hands down the best boba tea I’ve ever had!

Every sip was an experience, enhanced by the perfect balance of flavors and the unique jelly addition, which gave it an extra delightful twist. What truly sets this place apart is their mastery of boba pearls - not everyone gets it right, but these were flawlessly soft and perfectly cooked.

Beyond the tea, the ambiance, design, and service all reflected the owner's love for what they do, making it more than just a drink stop - it was an experience. Though I discovered this place by chance, I know it won’t be my last visit. From now on, this will be a must-stop every time I’m on my way to Charlotte!

Highly recommend to any boba lover or anyone looking for a fantastic, heartwarming tea experience.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you so much for this awesome review and highlighting your experience to share with others! We are so glad you enjoyed our bubble tea and hope to serve you again soon! 😊🧋
